frames.caption: A dramatic volcanic eruption spews molten lava high into the air, creating a vivid display of natural power. Thick plumes of dark smoke rise ominously, contrasting with the bright, fiery glow of the lava. The scene captures the raw, untamed energy of a volcanic landscape.
frames.description: The image depicts an active volcanic eruption in a rugged, mountainous landscape. Lava flows down the slopes, illuminating the surrounding area with its intense heat and light.

frames.caption: A plush toy resembling a volcano with a smiling face is humorously placed in front of an erupting volcano. The toy's vibrant orange and dark gray colors mimic the fiery eruption behind it, creating a playful juxtaposition.
frames.description: The scene depicts a plush toy styled as a volcano, set against the backdrop of a real volcanic eruption. The toy's cheerful expression contrasts with the dramatic natural setting.
